<p>To start a new task just click the <gui>New Task</gui> button and start writing. You do not need to save the task yourself â€“ GTG does that for you automatically while you write! Once you have completed the task, just click the <gui>Mark as Done</gui> button and the task will disappear from the GTG main window (you can still see it if you activate the <gui>Closed Task Pane</gui>). If the task is not relevant any more, simply click the <gui>Dismiss</gui> button to archive it.</p>

<p>You can learn all about various <app>GTG</app> features by exploring <link xref="index">the main page</link> of this <app>GTG</app> user manual.</p>

